text: haey se d ch noh ban mean bantoul tha chaur puok anak noam you so hv mk aoy yeung . haey nowpel del anakneasar ban mokadl you so hv you so hv ban pol tha chaur anak tralb towkean lokamcheasa robsa anak vinh haey suor keat ampi moulheto del sdrei ban chet dai khluoneng noh . pitabrakd nasa mcheasa robsakhnhom( a l laoh) doeng chbasa ampi ubayokl robsa puok neang
